%% ====================================================================
%% シーケンス図 05: 関係者追加 (公開範囲=STAKEHOLDERS への昇格を含む)
%% タスク管理システム v1.2
%% ====================================================================
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Owner as 所有者
  participant Browser as ブラウザ
  participant Sec as Spring Security
  participant Filter as TenantContextFilter
  participant Ctrl as TaskController
  participant UC as AddStakeholderUseCase
  participant AuthZ as TaskAuthorizationDomainService
  participant UserDir as LegacyUserDirectory<br/>(既存users)
  participant UTRepo as UserTenantRepository
  participant TaskRepo as TaskRepositoryImpl
  participant SHRepo as StakeholderRepositoryImpl
  participant Audit as AuditLogger
  participant DB as MySQL

  Owner->>Browser: タスク詳細 → 「関係者を追加」ボタン
  Browser->>Sec: POST /api/tasks/101/stakeholders<br/>{ "userId": 5 }
  Sec->>Filter: 認証OK (userId=1, role=MEMBER)
  Filter->>Ctrl: forward (TenantContext set)
  Ctrl->>UC: execute(taskId=101, userId=5, actor)

  UC->>TaskRepo: findById(101, tenantId=11)
  TaskRepo->>DB: SELECT * FROM tasks ...
  TaskRepo-->>UC: task (owner_id=1)

  UC->>AuthZ: assertVisibilityChangeable(task, userId=1)
  AuthZ->>AuthZ: task.ownerId == 1 ? → true
  AuthZ-->>UC: ✓ (所有者なので関係者操作可)

  Note over UC,UTRepo: 追加対象ユーザーが同テナント所属か検証
  UC->>UTRepo: findByUserAndTenant(userId=5, tenantId=11)
  UTRepo->>DB: SELECT FROM user_tenants WHERE user_id=5 AND tenant_id=11
  alt 所属していない
    DB-->>UTRepo: 0件
    UTRepo-->>UC: empty
    UC-->>Ctrl: throw NotInTenantException
    Ctrl-->>Browser: 400 E_VALIDATION<br/>"指定ユーザーはテナントに所属していません"
  else 所属
    DB-->>UTRepo: { user_id:5, role:MEMBER, status:ACTIVE }
    UTRepo-->>UC: ✓
  end

  Note over UC: 既存users から表示名を取得 (UI返却用)
  UC->>UserDir: findById(5)
  UserDir->>DB: SELECT id, full_name, email FROM users WHERE id=5<br/>(ReadOnly レプリカ)
  UserDir-->>UC: { id:5, fullName:"佐藤", ... }

  alt 現在の visibility が STAKEHOLDERS でない
    UC->>UC: 自動的に visibility を STAKEHOLDERS に昇格
    UC->>TaskRepo: save(task with visibility=STAKEHOLDERS)
    TaskRepo->>DB: UPDATE tasks SET visibility='STAKEHOLDERS' WHERE id=101
  end

  UC->>SHRepo: add(TaskStakeholder(taskId=101, userId=5, addedBy=1))
  SHRepo->>DB: INSERT INTO task_stakeholders<br/>(task_id, user_id, tenant_id, added_by, added_at)
  alt 既に登録済み (重複)
    DB-->>SHRepo: SQLIntegrityConstraintViolation
    SHRepo-->>UC: throw AlreadyStakeholderException
    UC-->>Ctrl: 409 Conflict
  else 新規追加
    DB-->>SHRepo: OK
    SHRepo-->>UC: TaskStakeholder
  end

  UC->>Audit: log(ADD_STAKEHOLDER, actor, taskId=101, addedUserId=5)
  Audit->>DB: INSERT audit_logs

  UC-->>Ctrl: Stakeholder
  Ctrl-->>Browser: 201 + Stakeholder JSON
  Browser-->>Owner: 関係者リストに追加表示<br/>(ユーザー5に通知メール送信予約)

  Note over UC,Audit: 関係者追加は所有者のみ実施可能 (NIST AC-3)<br/>visibility が自動昇格する場合は監査ログにも記録
